quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"Inna anzalnahu fee laylatialqadr"
  97,2,"Wama adraka ma laylatualqadr"
  97,3,"Laylatu alqadri khayrun min alfi shahr"
  97,4,"Tanazzalu almala-ikatu warroohufeeha bi-ithni rabbihim min kulli amr"
  97,5,"Salamun hiya hatta matlaAAialfajr"
  98,1,"Lam yakuni allatheena kafaroo min ahlialkitabi walmushrikeena munfakkeena hattata/tiyahumu albayyina"
  98,2,"Rasoolun mina Allahi yatloo suhufanmutahhara"
  98,3,"Feeha kutubun qayyima"
  98,4,"Wama tafarraqa allatheena ootooalkitaba illa min baAAdi ma jaat-humualbayyina"
  98,5,"Wama omiroo illa liyaAAbudooAllaha mukhliseena lahu addeena hunafaawayuqeemoo assalata wayu/too azzakatawathalika deenu alqayyima"
  98,6,"Inna allatheena kafaroo min ahli alkitabiwalmushrikeena fee nari jahannama khalideenafeeha ola-ika hum sharru albariyya"
  98,7,"Inna allatheena amanoowaAAamiloo assalihati ola-ika humkhayru albariyya"